headline: Can Nasdaq’s Recent Tech Partnerships Justify Its 13% 2025 Price Surge?
summary: Ever wondered if Nasdaq’s stock is truly worth its current price, or if there is untapped value beneath the surface? While the share price has edged up 0.7% over the past week, it has also seen a 13.2% gain year-to-date, indicating signs of growth potential. Recently, Nasdaq’s stock has attracted investor attention following notable tech partnerships and major financial market developments. These events have provided new energy and context to recent price movements, leading to speculation...
